    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gases that contribute to the greenhouse effect, including water vapor, carbon dioxide (CO2), methane (CH4), ozone (O3), nitrous oxide (N2O), hydrofluorocarbons (HFCs), halogenated fluorocarbons (HCFCs), and perfluorinated carbons (PFCs).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
