            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>造成溫室效應的氣體，包括水蒸氣、二氧化碳(CO2)、甲烷(CH4)、臭氧(O3)、一氧化二碳(N2O)、氟氫氮化合物(HFCs)、氟氮烴(HCFCs)、以及全氟聚合物(PFCs)。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gassen die bijdragen aan het broeikaseffect, zoals waterdamp, koolstofdioxide (CO2), methaan (CH4), ozon (O3), lachgas (N2O), fluorkoolwaterstoffen (HFK's), gehalogeneerde fluorkoolstoffen (HCFK's) en perfluorkoolstoffen (PFK's).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
